Class Dinosaur

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Actor
game.ActorObj.Dinosaur
All Implemented Interfaces:
Capable, Printable, ActorInterface
Direct Known Subclasses:
Agilisaurus, Allosaur, Archaeopteryx, Stegosaur
public abstract class Dinosaur
extends Actor
An abstract class for creating dinosaurs initializes useful variables such as foodlevel, gender, behaviour for every type dinosaurs to use
Author:
Charles Tan Wei Wen
